##################################################################
Installation Notes:

unzip package end edit config.php, set options dependant on
your shoutcast server.
Upload(ftp) contents to directory on your website.

Usage:
open up index.php or whatever page you want the status to display on,
file must end with .php
enter in the following code wherever you want the status of your
shoutcast server displayed.
//------start sc status snippet-----
include('./sc_status.php');
//-----end sc status snippet-------

\ALL DONE/
>>EOF
